  '''
  usage: pytest [-h] [-s {nogizaka46,sakurazaka46,hinatazaka46}] [-o OUTPUT]
                [-i] [--include-offline] [-g GROUP] [-m [MEMBERS ...]]
                [--cleanup] [--lang {en,ja,zh-TW,zh-CN,yue}] [-v] [--blog]

  pysaka CLI - Sakamichi Series Media Scraper

  options:
    -h, --help            show this help message and exit
    -s {nogizaka46,sakurazaka46,hinatazaka46}, --service {nogizaka46,sakurazaka46,hinatazaka46}
                          Target Service (Group)
    -o OUTPUT, --output OUTPUT
                          Output directory for downloaded content
    -i, --interactive     Run in interactive wizard mode
    --include-offline     Include unsubscribed/past members
    -g GROUP, --group GROUP
                          Filter by Group ID
    -m [MEMBERS ...], --members [MEMBERS ...]
                          Filter by Member IDs
    --cleanup             Remove auth data and config files
    --lang {en,ja,zh-TW,zh-CN,yue}
                          Language (en, ja, zh-TW, zh-CN, yue)
    -v, --verbose         Enable verbose logging
    --blog                Enable Blog Backup mode (all groups supported)

  '''
